name: OkeeneaBeaconsFinder
summary: Interact with beacons from Okeenea Tech.
description:
OkeeneaBeaconsFinder allows you to interact with beacons from Okeenea Tech. You need an API key to use it. 
Information on how to obtain an API key will be available soon.
